title: DBZ Battle Of The Gods & Resurrection F (Faulconer)
description:
DISCLAIMER:

These are custom edits of both DBZ Battle Of The Gods & Resurrection F to include the original American Faulconer Funimation score. Battle Of The Gods has been done independently of myself by an editor called CZ, while I did Resurrection F.

We're experienced film editors who worked on these projects in our spare time, please download, enjoy, and as always, please support the official release!
